Changelog
=========

# 0.2.0 - 2019-12-11

Implemented requested style changes and bug fixes.

 * Increase search bar size. (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Make search bar style more consistent (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Fix search bar count bug (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Fix Tool showing as current for non-Tool pages (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Add attribution under each section for display pages. (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Move count on People Listing above spinner (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Add sub-header linking to each listing page. (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Tweak the sub-header menu (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Change organizations on person page to nest organizations. (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Add more padding for nested organizations (Taeber Rapczak)
 * Fix spacing on person page when top line hidden (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Fix hidden blank category spacing. (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Fix typo in hiding blank categories for projects (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Remove the reverse button from listing pages. (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Move counts on listing pages to under title. (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Hide all attributes that are None (Hunter Jarrell)
 * Fix spacing under Organization name. (Hunter Jarrell)


